                            <p class="lead mb-4">
                                Casa Mira is a vibrant and growing community of homeowners who value peace, security, and a close-knit neighborhood environment. Located in a prime area, we are committed to providing our residents with a safe, clean, and welcoming place to call home.
                            </p>
